This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Lars Hanisch <dvb@flensrocker.de>

Project's homepage:          https://github.com/flensrocker/vdr-plugin-sundtek

Latest version available at: https://github.com/flensrocker/vdr-plugin-sundtek

