(at your option) any later version.
See the file COPYING for more information.

Description:
This plugin handles some features provided by the libmedia from Sundtek.

- detection of plugged in/out Sundtek devices so the dynamite-plugin
  can attach/detach them

Services:
sundtek-Monitor-v0.1 [start|stop]
starts or stops the thread which is connected to mediasrv.
Your init-script for mediasrv should use it after start and before stop.

sundtek-Scan-v0.1
get current list of devices from mediasrv and attach them.
